\begin_layout Standard
We also define an algorithm for constructing a graph given a formula in
 modal CNF.
 It has been prooved that this algorithm generates a graph such that its
 automorphism have a one-to-one mapping with the formula's simmetries.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Later, we describe the modules implemented for detecting simmetries in descripti
on logics and study each one of these modules through a simple example.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Finally, we test our tool against ontologies obtained from the web that
 are used in reasoners, and present an analisis about the results: execution
 times, ontologies size, graphs size and number of simmetries detected.
\end_layout

